ght have different chances to success, I understand that... but as it stands now, there's only one way to beat it (war+cleric). And Im not saying that it's the most efficient way of progressing on content. Im saying that it's the ONLY mother fucking way!<br /><br />And that's lame.<br /><br /><br /><blockquote id="quote"><font size="1" face="trebuchet ms,tahoma" id="quote">quote:<hr height="1" noshade id="quote">Posted by Ulaquay<br />There are 2 classes that can heal, 3 that can tank, 4 that can slow, and 6 that can hurt the mob.. imo it all seems pretty fair.<hr height="1" noshade id="quote"></font id="quote"></blockquote id="quote"><br /><br />The problem is that the feature brought by one very class (cleric) and the feature brough by one other very class (warrior) is more important that the features brought by all the rest 12 classes combined! Does that seem pretty fair too?<br /><br /><br /><br />Yag.</span id="msg"></font></td>
